  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study examines the efficacy of Marcaine in post-operative pain reduction for patients&#xD;
      receiving breast reduction surgery. Patients who consent will be randomized to which breast&#xD;
      receives a Marcaine injection and the other breast will have saline injected. Pain will be&#xD;
      assessed one time post-operatively using a 1-10 pain scale.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
